              <p>A facsimile of <ref target="https://corpuscoranicum.de/de/manuscripts/823/page/2r?sura=37&amp;amp;verse=121">fol. 2r</ref> of this manuscript was included in Johann Möller palaeographic catalogue (<ref target="https://www.zotero.org/groups/corpuscoranicum_pub/items/itemKey/HKJKRF57" sameAs="HKJKRF57" type="zotero">Möller 1844</ref>, pl. XIII, No. 2) and is accessible as image no. 2.</p>
